Engine

public protocol Engine

The entry point for any game engine specialization. See Game Engine Specialization

    Provide a method for loading textures, should not be called directly as it is intended to provide a point for a specific Engine specialization to provide concrete low-level loading behaviour.

    Declaration

    Swift

    loader
